entries.femaleVariant: Some people just wanna be happy. What don't you get about that?
Look, this isn't the time or the place.
Why not? You never want to talk, you always find some excuse.
I want us to be something. I want to be a couple.
And I don't believe in going mono, you know that. Can't we just have fun? Look around.
Let's not ruin the evening. Please.
